data.description: Corner Lot with RV Parking. Just over 1500 sq ft, this 4 bedroom 2 bath has high vaulted ceilings, french doors leading to backyard, fireplace, tile flooring and a front facing kitchen. Not to mention the large master bedroom suite with private door to large covered back patio. Enjoy a second detected covered patio great for summer BBQs and extra concrete around home including RV parking. Call today for your private viewing!
